### subscribeToUser
# Subscribe to a user

POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/645144b228cb64e0a917f51a/subscribe?action=1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}


### getUser
# Get user by ID

GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/645144b228cb64e0a917f51a HTTP/1.1

### getUsers
# Get users by IDs

POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/ids HTTP/1.1


### getSubscribers
# Get the list of user's subscribers

GET http://localhost:3000/api/user/645144b228cb64e0a917f51a/subscribers HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
